Package: scICER
Type: Package
Title: Single-cell Inconsistency-based Clustering Evaluation
Version: 1.0.6
Authors@R: person("Xiaolong", "Cao", email = "atps@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: scICER implements a systematic and efficient workflow to evaluate clustering 
    consistency in single-cell RNA-seq data. It generates multiple cluster labels using 
    the Leiden algorithm, calculates pairwise similarity with Element-Centric Similarity (ECS), 
    and provides automated framework for finding consistent clusters. This R package is fully 
    compatible with Seurat objects and designed for seamless integration into Seurat workflows.
